Chapter.Section:
Accessing Small $AlgebraDisplayName $FunctionName is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic $AlgebraDisplayNameLowerCase models from orders $MinDomainSize to $MaxDomainSize.
The models are generated by Mace4 , using the definitions in Section .
Dependency This package has no dependencies on other GAP packages.
